<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Verify Your Email</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333333;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .email-container {
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 30px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      .header {
        text-align: center;
        padding-bottom: 20px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #eeeeee;
      }
      .logo {
        max-height: 60px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 30px 0;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #4285f4;
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 12px 30px;
        border-radius: 4px;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
      .verification-code {
        background-color: #f5f5f5;
        padding: 10px;
        border-radius: 4px;
        font-family: monospace;
        font-size: 18px;
        letter-spacing: 2px;
        text-align: center;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
      .footer {
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #777777;
        text-align: center;
        padding-top: 20px;
        border-top: 1px solid #eeeeee;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="email-container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Verify Your Email Address</h1>
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <p>Hello <%= name %>,</p>

        <p>
          Thank you for creating an account with
          <span style="color: #4285f4">TrendHub Shop</span>. To complete your
          registration and access all features, please verify your email address
          by clicking the button below:
        </p>

        <div style="text-align: center">
          <a href="<%= link %>" class="button">Verify Email Address</a>
        </div>

        <p>Or you can copy and paste the following link into your browser:</p>
        <p style="word-break: break-all; font-size: 12px"><%= link %></p>

        <p>
          If you didn't create an account with us, you can safely ignore this
          email.
        </p>

        <p>Best regards,<br /></p>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>This is an automated message, please do not reply to this email.</p>
        <p>If you need further assistance, please contact our support team.</p>
        <p>&copy; 2025 TrendHub Shop. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
